  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00001",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张氏扶几而睡，起立望门，王恢上，入门。张氏惊喜。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00002",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "我正在这里想念于你，你就回来了。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00003",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "我怕夫人惦念，特地回家看望于你！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00004",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "你这满面风尘，真真是可怜人也。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00005",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "今日里见郎君形容瘦损，乍相逢不由得珠泪飘零。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00006",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "娘子呀！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00007",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "提起了一年事犹如梦境，我与你且宽怀重话前因。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00008",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "可怜负弩充前阵，历尽风霜万苦辛。饥寒饱暖无人问，独自眠餐你独自行。可曾身体蒙伤损，",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00009",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "倒也还好。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00010",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "是否烽烟屡受惊。细思往事心犹恨，",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00011",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "生把鸳鸯两下分。终朝如醉还如病，苦依薰笼坐到明。去时陌上花如锦，今日楼头柳又青。可怜奴在深闺等，海棠开日我想到如今。",
      "text_length": 58
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00012",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "屈指算来又是一年多了，真真的难为你了！",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00013",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "门环偶响疑投信，市语微哗虑变生。因何一去无音信，不管我家中肠断的人。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00014",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "哎，这军中寄信多有不便，我在军中也是常常惦念娘子啊！",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00015",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "毕竟男儿真薄幸，误人两字是功名。甜言蜜语真好听，谁知都是那假恩情。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00016",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "啊，你不寄信于我，使我天天的挂念，反来埋怨于我，真真岂有此理！",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00017",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王恢生气，旁坐。张氏沉思。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00018",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "啊！是啊！连我也没有寄信于他，倒是我错怪他了。他乃是饱受风霜之人，不可难为于他，待我向前安慰他几句。啊，官人，官人，官人呐！",
      "text_length": 62
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00019",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "岂有此理！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00020",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "你回来也算是重圆破镜，休再要觅封侯辜负香衾。粗茶饭还胜那黄金斗印，愿此生常相守怜我怜卿。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00021",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "娘子啊！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00022",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "今日里庆团圆开怀畅饮！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00023",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "喔！吃酒啊，你等着。丫鬟。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00024",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "丫鬟暗上，暗笑，端酒具。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00025",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "说什么撇家园求取功名。从此后傍妆台安心任命，休再要提往事旧恨重申。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00026",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "丫鬟做手势，示意睡觉，张氏以袖拂丫鬟。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00027",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00028",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "见丫鬟这举动将我点醒！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00029",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "啊，娘子，我们结婚有多少日子了？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00030",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "我与你原只是三日的新婚。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00031",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀，这就不错了，我们久别胜新婚！丫鬟，你呀，也劳乏了，安歇去吧。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00032",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "丫鬟做手势，等酒盘。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00033",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "这酒宴么？明日再来收拾吧。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00034",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "啊，官人，这……",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00035",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "丫鬟点头，下。王恢牵张氏衣，张氏不理。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00036",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "娘子啊！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00037",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "料不想今日里重温梦枕，喜相逢怕离别是梦非真。趁天色正好是月明如镜，",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00038",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "劝痴郎莫情急且坐谈心。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00039",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "你与我坐在这里等我，待我去到房中收拾一番，我再来唤你！",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00040",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "你呀！忒意地麻烦了啊！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00041",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀呀！你看你如此情急，羞也不羞啊。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00042",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "笑",
      "speakers": [
        "王恢"
      ],
      "text": "啊！哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00043",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张氏搬椅。王恢作不悦色，旁坐，假睡，偷看。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00044",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "南梆子",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "被纠缠陡想起婚时情景，算当初曾经得几晌温存。我不免去安排罗衾绣枕，",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00045",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张氏收拾床帐。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00046",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "南梆子",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "莫负他好春宵一刻千金。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00047",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张氏见王恢睡状。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00048",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "南梆子",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "原来是不耐烦已经睡困，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00049",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张氏端酒盘下，上，收拾床帐。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00050",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "南梆子",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "待我来再与你重订鸳盟。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00051",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王恢偷看而笑，张氏扶王恢入帐。内鼓噪声。张氏惊出帐。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00052",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "丫鬟，有人问起你家老爷，说他不曾回来。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00053",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张氏开门，出门。内鼓噪声。王恢出帐，出门，下。张氏惊，拦阻。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00054",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "莫非他又到军前去了，待我将他赶回。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00055",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张氏走圆场。王恢上，张氏碰见，张氏扯住王恢衣。内喊声。张氏恍惚迷离，一扑两扑，倒地。王恢下。",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00056",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "一霎时顿觉得身躯寒冷，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00057",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张氏起立。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00058",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "回龙",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "没来由一阵阵扑鼻风腥。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00059",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "场上换无定河边、尸首纵横布景。张氏惊看。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00060",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄快三眼",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "那不是草间人饥乌坐等，还留着一条儿那青布衣巾。见残骸竟裹着模糊血影，最可叹箭穿胸刀断臂粉身糜体，临到死还不知为着何因。",
      "text_length": 59
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00061",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张氏到场左看。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00062",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄快三眼",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "那不是破头颅目还未瞑，又见那死人须还结坚冰。寡人妻孤人子谁来存问？这骷髅几万千全不知名。隔河流有无数鬼声凄警，听啾啾、和切切，似诉说、冤魂惨苦，愿将军罢内战及早休兵。耳边厢又听得刀声响震！",
      "text_length": 94
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00063",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "十六兵士自两边分上，同绕场，同下。王恢随上，点头招手。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00064",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "你不要走哇，你不要走！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00065",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四兵同赶上，张氏急下。四兵绕场同下。台上忽黑，换闺房布景，张氏扶几坐。丫鬟上。",
      "text_length": 39
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00066",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "丫鬟"
      ],
      "text": "想不到刚才打了一个盹儿，做了一好梦，报与夫人知道。哟，睡着了——",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00067",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张氏醒，揉眼，沉思，喜。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00068",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "丫鬟"
      ],
      "text": "乐了——",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00069",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张氏怒。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00070",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "丫鬟"
      ],
      "text": "生气，哎哟！夫人，我家老爷回来了！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00071",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张氏"
      ],
      "text": "哦，你家老爷回来了？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "80000025_e00072",
      "play_id": "80000025",
      "scene_id": "80000025_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
